{"tid":1680472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣撚] 全民起義！大家都係文宣組！死黑警，你咁樣係唔會令到我驚！","createTime":"2019-10-29T00:32:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T14:32:37.000Z","uid":30520,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"fe23d3e463a180a12609dbab2ce95577b837ff92","tid":1680472,"uid":30520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T00:32:51.000Z","msg":"<strong>(請幫推)</strong> 今個星期開始，克警陸續係全港十八區對文宣組進行暴力打壓，依排都有好多新聞可以睇到大量文宣手足被捕，捉完就告你非法張貼街招、刑事毀壞、甚至襲警等，阻止香港人發聲，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">滿佈白色恐怖</span></span>。以下有一啲建議，集思廣益，開放討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GOU5gro.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGOU5gro.png&h=8fea2966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家抽少少時間睇下，一齊分析，因為已經越嚟越多手足為連儂牆而犧牲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>解決方法一： <span style=\"color: orange;\">文宣式 Be Water</span></strong><br />\n連儂牆嘅地點唔一定係固定地點，總之多人流就得。傳統文宣地方主要係隧道、天橋，依啲地方本身<span style=\"color: red;\">撤退路線受限</span>，而家又有藍絲、克警、建制派日日mon住，實行「警民合作」，我方應採取<span style=\"color: red;\">敵進我退</span>方法，路邊電箱、燈柱、路牌、巴士站、甚至係港鐵鐵皮外牆、被裝修店舖，都可以變成我地嘅連儂牆，做到真正be water。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>解決方法二：<span style=\"color: orange;\">高速快閃</span></strong><br />\n本身係地區文宣組嘅手足，相信大家本身已經有一個比較熟悉、信任的團體一齊行動，如果冇都自己主動搵下。請大家提高警覺，盡量將行動維持十分鐘內（白車都可以7分鐘內到，克警係收到風後五分鐘都可以嚟到，你以為真係需要39分鐘？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，並且需要<span style=\"color: red;\">多名哨兵</span>係各出入口遠處睇住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>解決方法三： <span style=\"color: gold;\">全民起義</span></strong><br />\n每個人都係文宣組！全港十八區真正痴文宣嘅人其實好少！如果，大家每一個人，都可以係tg 文宣group下載幾張文宣/甚至求其係連登熱門post，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">平時得閒隨手痴係街</span></span>，返工返學痴幾張，放工放學又痴幾張，其實已經足以遍地開花！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只係需要紙同雙面膠（有能力嘅手足可以買噴膠，五金舖/文具店好多都有得賣）。<br />\n<br />\n我相信好多文宣組都係和理非，依排克警大濫捕大家都會好驚，可能會唔敢再出黎痴，以前要面對藍絲嘅非法行為（打人/捅人），而家仲要面對克警濫捕，目的好簡單，就係要和理非<span style=\"color: violet;\">滅聲</span>，製做<span style=\"color: violet;\">白色恐怖</span>，「驚你就唔好出街」。大家係唔可以驚，因為連儂牆真係幫到好多中年人、老年人了解資訊，唔係被TVB以及建制派洗腦！<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">區選即將到來，對家越係驚，越係代表我地做啱</span></span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nHi mon po狗：<br />\n<br />\n當最溫和的抗爭手段也容忍不下，出動黑社會/恐怖分子用暴力解決，究竟誰人在這次抗爭運動中向對方步步進逼，未免太過明顯吧。如果你們連如此溫和的表達意見方法也接受不了，難道你們是想將抗爭運動推到暴力的極端面嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OaJ2fMi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOaJ2fMi.gif&h=6ef6f3f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"41caf338a8e9d3887a328a915cb30587f2e9b3be","tid":1680472,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T00:33:04.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，追蹤長期民意，做份國際文宣，話比全世界聽， 5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFPyvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=ce575ff3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"5520fa2d10e24643aad879821174c6a0e2dbdd55","tid":1680472,"uid":114360,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T00:36:30.000Z","msg":"好文推推推<br />\n我地112見<br />\n出門即刻airdrop"},{"pid":"9478bc5c432bf30e6259f9871bc28d3951d02a67","tid":1680472,"uid":30520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T00:36:31.000Z","msg":"<strong>警突襲連儂隧道拘文宣組</strong><br />\n<br />\n觀塘道連接創紀之城一期與牛頭角的行人隧道，今日凌晨零時有十多名巿民在隧道內張貼文宣時，突有數十名防暴警員封鎖出入口，目擊者指警方在隧道內帶走多人，並且檢走一批證物。至凌晨1時半，防暴警又在附近宜安街截停八名青少年，有街坊指，該批青年只是路經，並沒任何破壞行動，質疑警方是針對青少年濫查濫捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191027/20794964\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191027%2F20794964&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFPyvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=1ea8db88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191027%2F20794964&h=4f871791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191027/20794964</a>"},{"pid":"dce7b04ae3e515eb0e53343b2b7a273bdf6d783a","tid":1680472,"uid":114360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T00:37:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a9b29d7c0b7aa672be06912e3a51fb4f995ad6","tid":1680472,"uid":120480,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T00:38:45.000Z","msg":"唔好曬咁多時間用黎刪野<br />\n貼完即走"},{"pid":"feafb5360dd7a3351a8cb3a2bb26913efece1ff8","tid":1680472,"uid":30520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T00:40:13.000Z","msg":"<strong>警突擊巡查牛頭角連儂隧道　凌晨至少帶走兩女一男　</strong><br />\n<br />\n反修例運動中部分示威者以連儂牆形式，在行人隧道、牆壁貼上文宣，向市民講解社會現況。觀塘道連接創紀之城一期與牛頭角的行人隧道，今日（27日）凌晨警方突擊巡查，防暴警員封鎖出入口，在隧道內帶走至少一人。據知被捕人涉在隧道張貼文宣。直至凌晨1時半，警員又在牛頭角截停8名市民，其中一人指自己只是回家路經，突然被警員截停，查身份證後放行，但有一男一女因沒帶身份證被帶走。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KS4tg9G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKS4tg9G.jpg&h=245aad05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/390902/逃犯條例-警突擊巡查牛頭角連儂隧道-凌晨至少帶走兩女一男\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F390902%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E8%AD%A6%E7%AA%81%E6%93%8A%E5%B7%A1%E6%9F%A5%E7%89%9B%E9%A0%AD%E8%A7%92%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E9%9A%A7%E9%81%93-%E5%87%8C%E6%99%A8%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91%E5%B8%B6%E8%B5%B0%E5%85%A9%E5%A5%B3%E4%B8%80%E7%94%B7&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFPyvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=d6378ffb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/390902/逃犯條例-警突擊巡查牛頭角連儂隧道-凌晨至少帶走兩女一男</a>"},{"pid":"4fe5ddbe6bd156a03d96209fc9e6b31170d7cf60","tid":1680472,"uid":53072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T00:42:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/afwGCau.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FafwGCau.jpg&h=9ffe0da3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8vDt1Ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8vDt1Ca.jpg&h=d6d1961c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CfMbZoR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCfMbZoR.jpg&h=5aeb56d9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mbfPL3T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmbfPL3T.jpg&h=fdb1d676&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P3MrOhe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP3MrOhe.jpg&h=d08572c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f031889f5d471cd9164c2107289b8a9aacab8d2c","tid":1680472,"uid":30520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T00:43:44.000Z","msg":"突發！天水圍西鐵站有多名手足做文宣被大量狗追<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1673444\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1673444</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dd61752ff95809a02ff8f9e98f3cee68eb550a08","tid":1680472,"uid":235875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T00:44:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"335e098079f6a6bd65c7669359e78f886d2a2cbb","tid":1680472,"uid":30520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T00:48:59.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"dc7e46c8a3315cda9b47f0a7193dc2dddc3b26d7","tid":1680472,"uid":30520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T00:49:09.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"0356f78b1c23648d918fe49d0ef9c72ae2cfdc08","tid":1680472,"uid":191613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T00:49:23.000Z","msg":"有用post"},{"pid":"fba5d9f85e59c3452791ef1c6c2e8c47232c6543","tid":1680472,"uid":185424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T00:49:49.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"2e3ae9826214d982b6366377688f0b71a8b8748d","tid":1680472,"uid":30520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T00:54:42.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"beb3a81d3ea05bde3d7ccc74cd3cf39c76438faf","tid":1680472,"uid":30520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T00:54:52.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"e6c21b184de252faa76ca448c52cf76a11306e8c","tid":1680472,"uid":72065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T00:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85737429511d74eb6af307934a2b24875702b51","tid":1680472,"uid":30520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T00:59:22.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"67c775501e684fff9c305da18203ad8095bad55e","tid":1680472,"uid":30520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T01:02:38.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"e9ab3fe4d64df7f793eef21faafa325d9279eeb6","tid":1680472,"uid":197086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T01:05:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e7415448950fae64ebef8c734e719ab756818f3d","tid":1680472,"uid":30520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T01:05:26.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"08103fa17e340ec0911fd7c19f16235f495a043c","tid":1680472,"uid":311337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T01:08:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"22d3517552fd10cc27cd97dcc9023366da26fcde","tid":1680472,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T01:08:50.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"f107b270a058d7e67dddfdaefccd0efc6df40339","tid":1680472,"uid":114360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T01:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到出面d無聊post上晒熱門 <br />\n唯有入黎繼續幫推"},{"pid":"de24ce73a0134583bebfc14129aa66f4a7e33cb8","tid":1680472,"uid":30520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f107b270a058d7e67dddfdaefccd0efc6df40339","tid":1680472,"uid":114360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T01:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到出面d無聊post上晒熱門 <br />\n唯有入黎繼續幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T01:12:10.000Z","msg":"多謝絲打你幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}